				<h1 class="entry-title">7 ‘IDEALBITE’ Diet Tips to Help You Shed Serious Fat FAST!</h1>
		
		<div class="post-info"></div>		<div class="entry-content">
			<!-- SimpleReach Slide Plugin Version: 0.7.6 -->
